Download TIGER shapes for New England Combined City and Town Areas

Source: R/new_england_combined_areas.R
tt_new_england_combined_areas.Rd

Download TIGER shapes for New England Combined City and Town Areas

Usage

tt_new_england_combined_areas(year = 2021)

Arguments

year

Integer year. Required. Years < 2012 are not currently supported.

Value

sf data.frame

Examples

tt_new_england_combined_areas()
